{"tid":1914490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【緊急緊急！一個潛水黑警正在周圍呃錢 求各方巴絲認人】推！","createTime":"2020-03-07T14:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T14:57:05.000Z","uid":131478,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"02dccaf679392a8196737446193cdb88e38addc7","tid":1914490,"uid":131478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:25:40.000Z","msg":"是咁的！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我朋友早排網上識到個男人，一開頭無咩野，個樣都正常正直樣，講野有文有路，之後為左博信任仲認左我frd做阿妹，互相建立左信任，仲會周不時出街，正直君子無毛手毛腳。識落去就好L怪，開始問佢借錢，講到自己全家死L哂，博取同情心，自己又有癌症又無屋企番，三個月黎愈借愈多，呃佢一月個陣會有錢還，結果潛L左水！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果，我frd走去起佢底，發現佢係警察黎，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要有老婆同仔，佢絕到六親不認而做過街老鼠兼老千！之後我frd走左去差館告9佢，先發現佢都比人通輯緊WTF！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以條友一直長住酒店，係為左避差佬，搞到要周街呃人錢黎生存CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以今次出呢個PO警剔各位巴絲小心此人，佢有金像獎級既演技，講大話講到呃埋自己咁出神入化，因為佢呃我frd有癌症，<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />甚至會扮埋手震嘔血等等⋯￼逃亡左大半年真係唔L簡單！佢而家仲係網上釣緊水魚啊，相信仲有不少受害人落搭，尤其廿歲出頭啲𡃁妹要小心啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好心男人大丈夫有錯就認啦，打就企定定啦！折墮到周街呃女人錢！仲要自己本身做左咁耐警察都知法犯法！唔信你避到一世！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有相！請各位巴絲認住呢條老千！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姓名：Eric Fung 馮x良<br />\n年齡：45歲<br />\n出沒地點：長期轉酒店住，多數油尖旺區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外型：身高175cm 高瘦型 經常着運動休閑服裝（Adidas/Nike)<br />\n*注意佢成日攞假名昆人eg: Andy,Wilson<br />\n**注意此人極多fb假ac<br />\n***注意此人經常話自己有法律知識假幫人<br />\n****注意此人中文程度極低，經常打殘體字同勁多錯字<br />\n*****注意此人吹水能力極強，如果不幸既你識到佢千萬不可相信佢講既任何一句說話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8abVjt0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8abVjt0.jpg&h=a4715d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V5gx581.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV5gx581.jpg&h=da5e24ab&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hkGez2n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhkGez2n.jpg&h=42b56bb3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b7FnJVJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb7FnJVJ.jpg&h=af76cab5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tbpsaAK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtbpsaAK.jpg&h=0863f424&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U10fjt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU10fjt4.jpg&h=eabc141a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n￼<br />\n￼<br />\n￼<br />\n￼<br />\n￼<br />\n￼"},{"pid":"0f06746e15c778ccea01009875a9b5558bb6ba07","tid":1914490,"uid":125168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:29:38.000Z","msg":"認你個fd做呀妹（45歲）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015cf9315e212da872a0e8e3c9ec2098ba90737e","tid":1914490,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a718b9a63ea63c904af6f5070f1ae2aacd2e0588","tid":1914490,"uid":215611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"停職警？通輯都可以照番